title: Buy Guild Planers - 900w
description: This Guild 650W Planer is perfect for your woodworking tasks. This reliable tool has a high power 650W motor, 2mm maximum cut depth and 10mm rebating depth making it suitable for trimming doors or levelling uneven wooden surfaces. It is fitted with two, 82mm universal fit, high speed steel blades, which rotate at 16,000rpm to give a smooth finish every time. The soft grip handle, offers enhanced comfort through prolonged use, and the handy dust bag, which can be fitted to the left or right chip ejection port, will collect any debris generated.
